      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean i get the thing about the old bottle, but i just bought a brand new pack of those basic artificial tears yesterday. i really don't have time to go to the clinic right now with my work schedule, and Honestly it doesn't feel that bad, just annoying. if i just use the new drops a few times a day, do you think that'll fix the redness and the crusting if it's just because of the screen time? it seems like a lot of effort for something that's probably just dryness.",
