      "content": "can u just tell me straight tho, is there any chance it's actually just dryness? i've read online that crusting can just be from the eyes drying out too much and the tears getting thick. if i use the drops every hour or so for the next 2 days and it doesn't get worse, i can just assume it was just the screen time right? i really just want to avoid the doctor if i can help it.",
